Look into the directory "doc/" for documentation on the ColdX Driver,
the ColdX Project and other instructions.

An email list is available, send 'subscribe' in a mail message to:

    coldstuff-request@cold.org

This will register you to the coldstuff list at:

    coldstuff@cold.org

Further information can be obtained from:

    http://www.cold.org/

Read any other README's which may exist in this directory before
continuing, please!

Known bugs/problems:

    * callers() causes a SEGV sometimes (but not always).  It is
      used in .debug() in coldcore, so you may want to remove this.
    * tasks() causes a SEGV most times.

